title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update 12 and more aircrafts
description:
In this video we will look at the latest announcements related to World Update 12: New Zealand and some other cool stuff which was announced yesterday during the livestream of Microsoft and Asobo for developers. In this stream new things coming to MSFS were discussed and as a surprise they also made public that the AN-225 will be released for MSFS later this month.
